column2: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z, p.clean, p.flags, z.z as photoz, z.zErr as photozErr, s.specObjID as specObjID, s.z as specz, s.zErr as speczErr, p.rowv as RowV, p.rowvErr as RowVErr, p.colv as ColV, p.colvErr as ColVErr, dbo.fPhotoFlagsN (p.flags) as note from Galaxy as p LEFT OUTER JOIN photoz as z ON z.ObjID = p.ObjID LEFT OUTER JOIN specObjAll as s ON s.bestObjID = p.ObjID WHERE (p.clean = #) AND ( (p.rowv*p.rowv) / (p.rowVerr*p.rowVerr) + (p.colv*p.colv) / (p.colvErr*p.colvErr) > #) AND z.z> #, z.zErr> #, s.z> #, s.zErr> #
